<HL>
   Collapse of the Soviet Coup:
   CNN Ratings Jump
   Due to Soviet Crisis
</HL>
<DATE>
08/22/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   TBSA TBSB
